data.description: This amazing home features 5 bedrooms with the primary suite downstairs, 2 of the bedrooms have walk in closets. Primary bath features double vanities with sink, separate tub and shower. Large kitchen with island and walk in pantry overlooks the beautiful backyard with your own private pool. RV gate, storage shed, large grassy area, and extend covered patio in the backyard as well. Close proximity to schools, freeways and shopping. Don't miss this one!
